reviewText: Fantistic concert with Rod Stewart. A must for fans. Good sound and picture quality

One of Rod's poorer efforts, its obvious that without a big band behind him, he is rather pedestrian,He should have spent some of his early wealth on having singing lessons, which may sound uncharitable, but true! Though all done and said, it's a cracker of a songlist! Though, not a patch, on , "Live at Albert Hall"!
